                      yields?</span
                    >
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">+</span>
                  </button>
                  <div
                    class="px-4 pb-3 hidden faq-answer text-sm text-gray-700"
                  >
                    Yes. Select the “Actual/365 (Canada T-bills)” basis, enter
                    the face value and either the price or the discount rate.
                    The calculator will compute yields consistent with Canadian
                    T-bill quoting practices, including an investment rate based
